headline: Wabtec Announces Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date
summary: PITTSBURGH, October 06, 2025--Wabtec Corporation (NYSE: WAB) announced it will report 2025 third quarter results before the U.S. financial markets open on October 22, 2025. The company will conduct a conference call to discuss those results with analysts and investors at 8:30 a.m. ET the same day. To listen to the call via webcast, visit Wabtec’s website at www.WabtecCorp.com and click on "Events & Presentations" in the "Investor Relations" section. An audio replay of the call will be available

headline: What to Expect From Westinghouse Air Brake Technologies' Q3 2025 Earnings Report
summary: Westinghouse Air Brake Technologies is expected to report its third-quarter results soon, with analysts projecting a double-digit increase in earnings.
